Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.53,0:00:49.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsui no Sora (Endsky)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.54,0:01:01.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does not human life continue eternally?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.99,0:01:07.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if one's body is destroyed, their life shall become motes of essence,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.44,0:01:12.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,which shall gather in a new body and live on.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.74,0:01:16.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What foolishness. Don't you get it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.01,0:01:20.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not just humans... but all life must come to an end.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.49,0:01:23.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so shall this universe come to an end as well...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.75,0:01:27.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're mistaken! Eternal life, the circle of metempsychosis, they are-
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.26,0:01:31.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am not mistaken. The mistaken one is you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.75,0:01:35.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know, I shall show you...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.94,0:01:37.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.06,0:01:43.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I shall introduce you to the most sublime experience in the world...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.65,0:01:48.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, stop it. Nooo!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.66,0:04:36.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mamiya, for the sake of the motes of essence which remain in me, I shall destroy this body.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.65,0:04:40.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that the world's end of which you speak may be held back...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.78,0:04:47.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Yukito! Wake up already!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.51,0:04:49.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to be late!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.09,0:04:52.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez, every morning you're like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.28,0:04:54.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's you, Kotomi...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.52,0:05:03.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, they're white today. The color of purity, how nice...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.43,0:05:06.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You pervert!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.95,0:05:12.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Kotomi. Kotomi. Kotomi!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.11,0:05:15.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you still mad?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.48,0:05:17.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because you're always such a pervert, that's why!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.84,0:05:20.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's my nature as a man, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.28,0:05:23.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's your nature as a man?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.04,0:05:25.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't understand my feelings at all...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.91,0:05:27.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What'd you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.85,0:05:33.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, just now, I couldn't hear you... what did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.26,0:05:34.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, Yukito... over there...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.84,0:05:36.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.56,0:05:39.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Police cars... and is that an ambulance?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.93,0:05:41.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.93,0:05:43.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kotomi, let's go check it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.17,0:05:49.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kotomi...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.43,0:05:53.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yukito... why did something like this happen...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.98,0:05:59.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seems like Zakuro was killed by falling from the rooftop.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.11,0:06:02.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I hear the police are treating it as a suicide.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.80,0:06:05.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But she wasn't acting suicidal...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.14,0:06:09.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it were a suicide, wouldn't she ordinarily have left a note or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.94,0:06:13.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, but I hear she was really popular with the guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.20,0:06:15.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could it have been a jealous lover?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.93,0:06:20.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But there wasn't any sign of a struggle on the rooftop.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.76,0:06:33.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Attention. We will be holding an assembly of the whole school.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.03,0:06:36.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All students, please come to the school yard.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.51,0:06:37.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will repeat...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.31,0:06:57.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, today's pretty gloomy...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.37,0:07:02.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't even remember anything from class...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.87,0:07:08.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kotomi, cheer up...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.77,0:07:11.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess that's an absurd thing to ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.86,0:07:15.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, Zakuro was your friend, and now she's dead...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.44,0:07:19.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And on top of that, no one knows why...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.36,0:07:28.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yukito... thanks for worrying about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.21,0:07:30.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm all right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.61,0:07:32.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kotomi...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.08,0:07:39.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I said I'm okay, didn't I? Anyway, I have club activities, so go home ahead of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.90,0:07:43.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Club activities? At a time like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.80,0:07:51.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Before my mood gets any worse, I'm gonna try working up a sweat.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.30,0:07:56.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand, Kotomi. Let it all out.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.68,0:08:01.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, let's go home together today. I'll be waiting here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.02,0:08:05.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, Yukito. Then, see you later!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.80,0:10:49.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing over there, Yokoyama?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.96,0:10:51.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and change.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.93,0:10:56.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, yes. I'm sorry. I'll get changed right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.81,0:11:01.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zakuro, just what happened to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.79,0:11:06.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,None of us know what to believe anymore...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.42,0:11:10.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kotomi, who was always so cheerful until yesterday, is so sad...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.69,0:11:26.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Minakami. Are you thinking of Takashima?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.46,0:11:28.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.57,0:11:31.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The circle of metempsychosis. Endsky.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.37,0:11:34.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? Ayana, what are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.74,0:11:38.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mamiya hasn't come to school lately, has he?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.40,0:11:46.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, Mamiya? Isn't he the biggest loner in our class?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.39,0:11:48.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what happened to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.39,0:11:50.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've seen him once in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.27,0:11:52.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? So he has come to school?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.96,0:11:55.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, but not to the classroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.68,0:11:56.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then where?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.83,0:11:59.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not really certain, but probably...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.27,0:12:05.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, whatever. Besides that, Ayana, do you know anything about Zakuro?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.32,0:12:10.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm. Seems like she had something to do with Mamiya...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.02,0:12:12.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With Mamiya? What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.32,0:12:17.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mamiya... was involved in something weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.19,0:12:19.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Endsky, or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.77,0:12:23.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Endsky? What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.11,0:12:29.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know either. But, Mamiya was definitely obsessed with some strange idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.85,0:12:30.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Strange idea?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.82,0:12:36.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. It seems like he approached Takashima about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.60,0:12:42.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, when she returned to the classroom after talking to him,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.15,0:12:46.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,she was just studying normally with everyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.05,0:12:49.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something like that happened, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.06,0:12:52.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But what does that have to do with her committing suicide?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.43,0:12:56.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not sure. But, you had better be careful of Mamiya.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.14,0:13:00.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once in a while, he has these scary eyes...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.21,0:13:09.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Yukito. I made you wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.39,0:13:12.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seems like you cheered up.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.19,0:13:14.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. A little, now that I've sweated it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.96,0:13:16.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shall we head back?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.48,0:13:26.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kotomi, sorry about this morning. I was just messing with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.45,0:13:32.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you buy me a hamburger, I'll forgive you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.52,0:13:33.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh u!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.24,0:13:36.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,'Cause I'm already hungry...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.77,0:13:39.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kotomi's holding in her sadness...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.36,0:13:43.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood. Let's go get a combo!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.30,0:13:47.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yukito, I love you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.44,0:13:52.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Yasuko Yokoyama went missing in the night?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.77,0:13:59.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems like it. Her parents just came to school, along with the police...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.73,0:14:02.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kotomi, did you notice anything odd about her during your club?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.36,0:14:08.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, nothing. We were just practicing on our own as usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.45,0:16:40.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm? Ah... where's Kotomi?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.98,0:16:45.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's always here to yell at me in that energetic voice...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.26,0:16:48.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I guess it's my turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.08,0:16:55.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Yukito.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.02,0:16:59.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Morning. Is Kotomi still asleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.01,0:17:00.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.02,0:17:01.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.07,0:17:05.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the evening, she got a phone call from Yokoyama in her kendo club...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.83,0:17:08.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She went to meet her, and she still hasn't come back...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.94,0:17:10.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,wat?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.30,0:17:14.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something strange is going on at your school...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.65,0:17:17.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And she's gotten involved in it...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.95,0:17:20.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Call the cops, lady!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.23,0:17:22.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna go check it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.94,0:17:37.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ayana!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.47,0:17:40.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Minakami. Morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.01,0:17:45.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ayana! Tell me where Mamiya is!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.79,0:17:48.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.45,0:17:50.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you so worked up?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.70,0:17:55.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kotomi's gone missing this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.58,0:17:58.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Kotomi is missing?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.52,0:18:02.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I just had her mom call the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.58,0:18:06.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Ayana. Where has Mamiya gone?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.41,0:18:09.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not positive, but I think he's... at the pool.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.97,0:18:11.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The pool?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.05,0:18:15.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. When the indoor pool was built, the outdoor pool was retired.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.52,0:18:18.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no water in it right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.03,0:18:23.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I saw Mamiya go down into the drainage channel of it once...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.13,0:18:27.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's it! Ayana, I'm going on ahead! Explain things to the police!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.48,0:19:13.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Very well, that's enough! Now have a taste of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.66,0:19:15.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nooo!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.31,0:19:21.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cry just like that! No one's going to come save you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.70,0:19:23.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fuck you, Mamiya!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.83,0:19:25.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Minakami, why are you here...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.69,0:19:26.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yukito...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.67,0:19:31.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You freak! Do you understand what you've done?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.85,0:19:36.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Endsky...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.29,0:19:37.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.65,0:19:40.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can see it... Endsky...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.04,0:19:44.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Endsky is... that which visits the eternal darkness...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.52,0:19:46.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mamiya... you...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.57,0:19:48.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't you see it, Minakami?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.92,0:19:52.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look... it's right over there... Endsky...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.36,0:19:54.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're nuts...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.53,0:19:59.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zakuro? Is that Zakuro?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.33,0:20:06.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't come! Don't come near me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.78,0:20:09.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mamiya, it's all right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.48,0:20:12.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is not a world of eternal darkness...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.33,0:20:16.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Endsky is... the way it has been from the beginning...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.88,0:20:21.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This universe... has no beginning, nor end...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.06,0:20:28.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lies, lies! It will end! It must!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.47,0:20:35.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kotomi, are you all right!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.98,0:20:37.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Thank you, Yukito.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.90,0:20:39.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It must have been scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.15,0:20:43.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, when you came to rescue me, Yukito...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.16,0:20:45.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was really happy... thank you...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.65,0:20:47.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a little embarrassing...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.42,0:20:51.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is your reward for protecting me...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.51,0:20:53.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give myself to you...
